{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLInputElement: selectionchange イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/selectionchange_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement\"><code>HTMLInputElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/files\"><code>files</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/labels\"><code>labels</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/multiple\"><code>multiple</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/webkitdirectory\"><code>webkitdirectory</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/webkitEntries\"><code>webkitEntries</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/checkValidity\"><code>checkValidity()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/reportValidity\"><code>reportValidity()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select\"><code>select()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setCustomValidity\"><code>setCustomValidity()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setRangeText\"><code>setRangeText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setSelectionRange\"><code>setSelectionRange()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/showPicker\"><code>showPicker()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/stepDown\"><code>stepDown()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/stepUp\"><code>stepUp()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event\"><code>invalid</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/search_event\"><code>search</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select_event\"><code>select</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>selectionchange</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div>\n<p>\n  <strong><code>selectionchange</code></strong> は<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Selection\">選択 API</a> のイベントで、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 要素の中でテキストの選択状態が変化したときに発行されます。\n  これは、文字単位の選択範囲位が変化した場合も、キャレットが移動したときも含みます。\n</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th>バブリング</th>\n      <td>はい</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>キャンセル</th>\n      <td>不可</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>インターフェイス</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>イベントハンドラープロパティ</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/selectionchange_event\" title=\"onselectionchange\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>onselectionchange</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>このイベントは通常 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 上にイベントリスナーを追加し、ハンドラー関数内で <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement\"><code>HTMLInputElement</code></a> の <code>selectionStart</code>, <code>selectionEnd</code>, <code>selectionDirection</code> の各プロパティを読み取ることで処理します。</p>\n<p>また、グローバルな <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/selectionchange_event\" title=\"onselectionchange\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>onselectionchange</code></a> イベントハンドラーにリスナーを追加し、ハンドラー関数内で <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document/getSelection\"><code>Document.getSelection()</code></a> を使って<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Selection\" title=\"選択状態\">選択状態</a>を得ることもできます。しかし、これはテキストの選択範囲の変更を取得するのにはあまり便利ではありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の例は、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 要素の中にあるテキストの選択状態を取得する方法を示しています。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Enter and select text here:<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>mytext<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rows</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cols</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>selectionStart: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>start<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>selectionEnd: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>end<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>selectionDirection: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>direction<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> myinput <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mytext\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmyinput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"selectionchange\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"start\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myinput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>selectionStart<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"end\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myinput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>selectionEnd<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"direction\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myinput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>selectionDirection<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"結果","title":"結果","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例\" id=\"frame_examples\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/selectionchange_event/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":